課程教材 Course Material


參考書目 References
	    1. Magill, Richard A. (2011). Motor learning and control: concepts and applications. 9th Edition, McGraw-Hill, 2011.
2. Latash ML. Fundamentals of motor control. Elsevier, 2012. 
